scripts.start: npm run check && cross-env NODE_ENV=dev webpack-dev-server --config config/webpack.dev.config.js --color --progress --inline --open
scripts.build: npm run check && cross-env NODE_ENV=dev webpack --config config/webpack.pro.config.js --color --progress
scripts.build-xdmt: npm run check && cross-env NODE_ENV=dev cross-env APP_NAME=xdmt webpack --config config/webpack.pro.config.js --color --progress
scripts.online: npm run check && cross-env NODE_ENV=pro webpack --config config/webpack.pro.config.js --color --progress
scripts.online-xdmt: npm run check && cross-env NODE_ENV=pro webpack cross-env APP_NAME=xdmt --config config/webpack.pro.config.js --color --progress
